Text: The dialogue system that helps you managing your conversations.
This Dialogue system comes with a Custom Editor, you can Import/Export as CSV and manager the dialogues speakers.
What do you want to know more about?
Dialogue editor has a very intuitive tree structure for you manage the conversation flow.
Is implemented with the latest Unity Undo system, that way you will never lose any work. Just press Ctrl + Z to Undo a change.
Also the Dialogue editor automatically saves your work when the window is closed.
In Dialogue Editor you can Export the dialogue in CSV to help you translate the conversation.
After that just Import the translated CSV in the Dialogue Editor and it will restore it.
Speaker like the name sugests, the element that is speaking the line of the dialogue.
It was implemented using ScriptableObjects for more flexibility
That way you just need to define the Speker once and use in many conversations.
Thanks a lot for listen, I hope this help you.
